undary conditions. A key ingredient of our analysis is the\nrenormalisation technique of arXiv:1404.7257 to estimate the spectral gap of\nthe East process. Here we extend this technique to get the main asymptotics of\na suitable principal Dirichlet eigenvalue of the process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Dec 2021 18:15:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Feb 2022 09:05:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 10 Nov 2022 00:38:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-11"}
